Author: paranormalpleb
Text: When I experienced this the thought of food made me gag.  Right.  In.  Front.  Of.  My.  Mother.  She still did not know at least, but I had a few bites of food, just for her, and I felt AWFUL.  For hours I laid on the couch and tried to ignore the pains.

Author: lhadnil
Text: me all of yesterday. sometimes i even throw up... always feel better when i keep up with my electrolytes and eat a little something  but yeah yesterday i went to bed at 8pm lol
